install script:
  if production
  add systemd unit (then add enable/start to provision)
  add joblist port from env.JOBLIST_PORT
  add ipp port from env.IPP_PORT

persistence:
  fs.open(path.join( os.tmpdir(), Math.random() ), 'w+', callback(err,fd))
  keep fd around
  fs.unlink(thepath)
  create read/write stream from fd, turn off autoclose - let shutdown or forget close
  pipe stream from job to file

joblist:
  works with new persistence

joblist template:
  give job extension/mimetype using module mmmagic
  pug/pug-browser
  download/forget links
  js to send delete

client side error reporting:
  add put/post for client errors to send them serverside
